Eminem, it had a point in the 90's, early 2000's but not now. I think there are more advantages to NOT use RAR than to use it now. bittorrent comes with built in hash check making sfv irrelevant. And I don't want samples. If you skip packing the files I can choose to not download the sample. Besides todays, games, movies, applications and music etc already use heavy compression so packing seldom makes the files smaller.
If someone could seed this for me, I'd be eternally grateful. Thanks!
